    "description": "Piala Inc. provides marketing services in Japan. It offers e-commerce digital transformation services for the healthcare, beauty, and food industries, as well as services for the entertainment industry. The company provides business, product, infrastructure development, and branding services. The company also offers KPI guarantee service, mail order digital transformation service, CM-UP for TV commercial effectiveness, Offline DX linking offline and web advertising, influencer casting through Buzz Minutes, official SNS account management via BuzZeal, live commerce with LiveBuzz, middle funnel video and influencer campaigns, LINE communication support, infomercials, and consulting. In addition, it provides BEATMAKER, financial support with PIALAPAY, and entertainment industry solutions via the CYBER STAR platform, which offers live streaming, fan club management, e-commerce for content and merchandise, electronic ticket sales, and data analysis. Piala Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Shibuya, Japan."
